            <title>薪酬談判未達共識   Samsung 電子工會或 55 年來首次罷工</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/08/worker-strike-looms-over-samsung-as-salary-negotiations-falter/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=worker-strike-looms-over-samsung-as-salary-negotiations-falter</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/08/worker-strike-looms-over-samsung-as-salary-negotiations-falter/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美鳳]]>
            </dc:creator>
